{"tha-ap485:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap485:0.2":"Pamsukulavagga ","tha-ap485:0.3":"Bhisadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap485:1.1":"“Ogayha yam pokkharanim, ","tha-ap485:1.2":"nanakunjarasevitam; ","tha-ap485:1.3":"Uddharami bhisam tattha, ","tha-ap485:1.4":"ghasahetu aham tada. ","tha-ap485:2.1":"Bhagava tamhi samaye, ","tha-ap485:2.2":"padumuttarasavhayo; ","tha-ap485:2.3":"Rattambaradharo buddho, ","tha-ap485:2.4":"gacchati anilanjase. ","tha-ap485:3.1":"Dhunanto pamsukulani, ","tha-ap485:3.2":"saddamassosaham tada; ","tha-ap485:3.3":"Uddham nijjhayamanoham, ","tha-ap485:3.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap485:4.1":"Tattheva thitako santo, ","tha-ap485:4.2":"ayacim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap485:4.3":"‘Madhum bhisehi savati, ","tha-ap485:4.4":"khiram sappim mulalibhi. ","tha-ap485:5.1":"Patigganhatu me buddho, ","tha-ap485:5.2":"anukampaya cakkhuma’; ","tha-ap485:5.3":"Tato karuniko sattha, ","tha-ap485:5.4":"oruhitva mahayaso. ","tha-ap485:6.1":"Patigganhi mamam bhikkham, ","tha-ap485:6.2":"anukampaya cakkhuma; ","tha-ap485:6.3":"Patiggahetva sambuddho, ","tha-ap485:6.4":"aka me anumodanam. ","tha-ap485:7.1":"‘Sukhi hotu mahapunna, ","tha-ap485:7.2":"gati tuyham samijjhatu; ","tha-ap485:7.3":"Imina bhisadanena, ","tha-ap485:7.4":"labhassu vipulam sukham’. ","tha-ap485:8.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap485:8.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap485:8.3":"Bhikkhamadaya sambuddho, ","tha-ap485:8.4":"ambarenagama jino. ","tha-ap485:9.1":"Tato bhisam gahetvana, ","tha-ap485:9.2":"agacchim mama assamam; ","tha-ap485:9.3":"Bhisam rukkhe lagetvana, ","tha-ap485:9.4":"mama danamanussarim. ","tha-ap485:10.1":"Mahavato vutthahitva, ","tha-ap485:10.2":"sancalesi vanam tada; ","tha-ap485:10.3":"Akaso abhinadittha, ","tha-ap485:10.4":"asaniya phalantiya. ","tha-ap485:11.1":"Tato me asanipato, ","tha-ap485:11.2":"matthake nipati tada; ","tha-ap485:11.3":"Soham nisinnako santo, ","tha-ap485:11.4":"tattha kalankato ahum. ","tha-ap485:12.1":"Punnakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap485:12.2":"tusitam upapajjaham; ","tha-ap485:12.3":"Kalevaram me patitam, ","tha-ap485:12.4":"devaloke ramim aham. ","tha-ap485:13.1":"Chalasitisahassani, ","tha-ap485:13.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap485:13.3":"Sayam patam upatthanti, ","tha-ap485:13.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap485:14.1":"Manussayonimagantva, ","tha-ap485:14.2":"sukhito homaham sada; ","tha-ap485:14.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap485:14.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap485:15.1":"Anukampitako tena, ","tha-ap485:15.2":"devadevena tadina; ","tha-ap485:15.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap485:15.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap485:16.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap485:16.2":"yam bhisam adadim tada; ","tha-ap485:16.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap485:16.4":"bhisadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap485:17.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap485:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap485:17.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap485:18.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap485:18.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap485:18.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap485:19.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap485:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap485:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap485:20.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhisadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap485:21.1":"Bhisadayakattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}